y, no white pith, finely grated","40 g lime juice (approx. 2 limes)"]},{"title":"Cheesecake filling","content":["40 g unsalted butter, plus extra for greasing","125 g Granita biscuits (½ packet)","300 g white chocolate, broken into pieces","500 g cream cheese, cut into pieces and softened","50 g caster sugar","1 tsp vanilla bean paste","4 eggs","1000 g water"]}],"id":"r70988","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-2pIOgrRzrI0\/XZanJOMYj6I\/AAAAAAAAg6s\/loktW7IbAAgK-x3CIUpxPBAneU0W_A-_ACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_3MQitJDVZ87xuFmY.png","title":"Steamed white chocolate cheesecake","publishedAt":"2015-08-07T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"8.7 g","fat":"28 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"31 g","calories":"1689 kJ \/ 402 kcal"},"usefulItems":"sealable container, springform cake tin (19 cm), baking paper, paper towel, small bowl, refrigerator, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Decorate your cake with thin slices of fresh mango or lime.","For a different flavour, replace mango and lime coulis with <i>Kiwi coulis<\/i> (see recipe on this recipe chip) or <i>Berry coulis<\/i> (see <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i>)."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","25h 20m","12 portions"]}